creator: Mansa Infotech
descriptionHtml:
Power up local savings and live Concierge service at your fingertips! Enrolled members can use this app to access their exclusive membership benefits quickly and conveniently. It’s like having a Personal Mobile Concierge® on your android.

Members will enjoy savings, discounts, and rebates on products and services they use every day along with the security of their exclusive Identity Theft Restoration Rescue® program. And with nearly 300,000 participants from coast to coast, you’ll save like never before. Membership benefits include substantial savings at local and national chain restaurants, local and national retail businesses, on gas and groceries, on movie tickets and entertainment, travel reservations services, health and beauty services, home and garden purchases, and so much more. And your personal live Concierge is just a tap away ready to provide the personal assistance you need and deserve!

Just tap, show, and save all over town!

Features:
Nearly 300,000 discount participants
Identity Theft Restoration Rescue® program
GPS location search to navigate deals nearby or wherever you travel
No coupons – just tap, show, and save
eGift Cards are sent immediately to your android for instant redemption
Dining Dough program saves up to 87% on dining certificates accepted at face value
My Savings tallies the amount you’ve saved
Complete full service travel with discounts and rebates
Concierge services provided by live representatives

Questions, comments, and suggestions? Send us a message at info@GenGold.net or call us at 1.800.428.6686.

Download the free app, enter your username and password which can be obtained from our full website, and save all over town, and all over the country!

Special Note: This app is currently available only to registered members and not available to the general public. For information on how to join, please contact us.
